        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The female mechanoid does not answer immediately, instead raising her eyes to survey her surroundings.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 40,
        "ActionId": 40,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The once-standing buildings have all crumbled to ruins in the riot, while her rage continues to intensify.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 41,
        "ActionId": 41,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500920', 3: '5', 4: '-550'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 42,
        "ActionId": 42,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Veronica', 3: 'Did they escape, or did you let them go?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 43,
        "ActionId": 43,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Veronica', 3: 'They were being held in the spacecraft docking area. Even with some combat capability, that Construct wouldn\\'t be able to breach the gates there.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 44,
        "ActionId": 44,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Veronica', 3: 'Not to mention that the Administrative Hall\\'s security codes are nearly impossible to crack... You\\'re telling me that they escaped just like that?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 45,
        "ActionId": 45,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Aleksei', 3: 'Cough. Please don\\'t be angry, Veronica.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 46,
        "ActionId": 46,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'On the other end of the line, Aleksei speaks with an unfamiliar emotion that Veronica doesn\\'t recognize, his tone completely indifferent.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 47,
        "ActionId": 47,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Veronica', 3: 'You have one minute to explain yourself.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 48,
        "ActionId": 48,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Aleksei', 3: 'Sigh. I didn\\'t want this either, but your associate—Hanying—rescued them. The autonomous mechanoids and I tried our best to stop her.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 49,
        "ActionId": 49,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Aleksei', 3: 'But... Hanying is completely devoted to the humans. She single-handedly took down both me and the autonomous mechanoids.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 50,
        "ActionId": 50,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Aleksei', 3: 'A mechanoid of such power... I\\'m no match for her.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 51,
        "ActionId": 51,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'He shakes his head with an exaggerated display of sorrow.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 52,
        "ActionId": 52,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Veronica', 3: 'Hanying...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 53,
        "ActionId": 53,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Veronica', 3: '...Hah, how absurd. So she\\'s made a deal with that commandant and sided with the humans now?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 54,
        "ActionId": 54,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'She sneers.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 55,
        "ActionId": 55,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Aleksei', 3: 'Veronica, I\\'m different from her... You know I\\'m on your side.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 56,
        "ActionId": 56,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Aleksei', 3: 'That\\'s why I must warn you, Veronica, as your loyal friend.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 57,
        "ActionId": 57,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Aleksei', 3: 'Bifrost is entering its final charging phase. We can\\'t afford any mistakes now.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 58,
        "ActionId": 58,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 203,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '2', 2: '0.25', 3: '550'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 59,
        "ActionId": 59,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'He turns to show the screen behind him through the comms feed. The lengthy loading process is nearly complete.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 60,
        "ActionId": 60,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Veronica', 3: 'I don\\'t need you to remind me of that.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 61,
        "ActionId": 61,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Aleksei', 3: 'To build our new world, we must eliminate any possibility of human interference.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 62,
        "ActionId": 62,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Aleksei', 3: 'You know how humans are—always selfish, always arrogant, forever dreaming of eradicating those different from them and ruling this world.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 63,
        "ActionId": 63,
        "NextActionId": null,
